# Lead generation

Follow `.cursor/skills/lead-generation-form-pages/SKILL.md` when adding or editing lead-gen scrapers.

## Hard rules

- Product BE handlers return `ALApiResponse<LeadItem[]>` with `id` on each item — no FE response mappers in `lead-gen-api.ts`.
- `lead-gen-api` switch cases are direct `apiClient.post` calls (same shape as Maps / Instagram / LinkedIn).
- Always pass `creditModule` into `LeadFormWrapper`.
- Register costs only in `CREDIT_COST_PER_ITEM` / `getCreditCostPerItem`.
- Debit only in `createUserLeads` after a successful scrape.
- Hide credits UI for admins / `creditsExempt` users.
- Colocate form defaults and select option arrays in the route `_constants.ts`.
